                            <para>If voltage is missing check for blown fuse #10 and check for open or short in circuit
                                12 BLK 18.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>Connector C7, cavity 2 to cavity 3</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colspan="2" spanname="S2T3" align="center">
                            <para>12 &#177; 1.5 volts</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colspan="3" spanname="S4T6" align="center">
                            <para>If voltage is missing check for open or short in circuits 16 BLU 10 and 12 BLU 10.
                            </para>
                            <para>If rear destination sign illuminates during this test, replace destination sign
                                switch.
                            </para>
                            <para>If circuits test good and lights still fail, test circuits at bulbs.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
